{
  "texts": [
    "This proves E ⊂ E i 0 ↓ j 0.",
    "The opposite inclusion being always true, we proved E = E i 0 ↓ j 0.",
    "(ii) ⇔ (iii) Let s ∈ E max then there exists t ∈ E i 0 j 0 such that s ⊂ t. Since s is maximal for inclusion in E, s = t and therefore s ∈ E i 0 j 0.",
    "Conversely if E max ⊂ E i 0 j 0 then E i 0 ↓ j 0 ⊃ E max↓ = E.(iii) ⇒ (i).",
    "Conversely assume that E = E i 0 ↓ j 0."
  ]
}